{{unreferenced|date=July 2018}} {{Infobox journal | cover = | editor = | language = [[German language|German]] | discipline = [[Human geography]] | frequency = Quarterly | abbreviation = | impact = | impact-year = | publisher = [[Franz Steiner Verlag]] | country = [[Germany]] | history = 1895-present | website = http://www.steiner-verlag.de/GZ/ | link1 = | link1-name = | ISSN = 0016-7479 | eISSN = | OCLC = }} The '''''Geographische Zeitschrift''''' (English: ''The Geographical Journal'') is a [[Germany|German]] [[Peer review|peer-reviewed]] [[academic journal]] specialising in [[human geography]]. It was established in 1895 and is now published by the [[Franz Steiner Verlag]].
